{"tid":1578330,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"921唔好同何妖正面衝突，重建連儂牆改922","createTime":"2019-09-18T05:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T15:37:45.000Z","uid":15314,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"f737a54f45fcf3ce56cff5ce0bbf80fc26d571e8","tid":1578330,"uid":15314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"藍絲同何妖係抵打，死十次都唔夠<br />\n但係！！佢地只係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢場運動對家既卒仔</span><br />\n寧願你地留返啲氣力同被捕quota喺真正對黑警／政府既戰場<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">藍絲活動一定冇我地咁密同咁有恆心</span></span><br />\n而且好多都係收錢先出，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">根本唔會出得好多次</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">由佢地班傻西自high行完咪算<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n亦見到有文宣話918重建連儂牆<br />\n無謂我地岩岩先重建完<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n921又俾佢地撕走哂，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好自動送上金錢同時間</span></span><br />\n<br />\n平時藍絲落單未必敢係連儂牆打我地<br />\n就算打，我地增援既人都多<br />\n但係當日係佢地自發既活動，情況就會調返轉<br />\n我好贊成私了hit and run<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但<span style=\"color: red;\">當日佢地增援既人會較多，<br />\n就算佢地唔夠你揪，但人多阻住唔俾你走<br />\n大家<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">hit到都未必run到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n唔係阻咁多位勇武上場，但為左佢地冒險真係唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我地一齊922重建連儂牆好唔好呀！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ce5270a151b53866a9e5c276aea635e7384f1a8","tid":1578330,"uid":311275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"撕一貼十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40bc2cb420f9c8535b2b168fa03353146c72d1b5","tid":1578330,"uid":67332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:57:56.000Z","msg":"<code>唔打頭頸，唔用利器，對方有武器就先發制人，對方冇刀就唔好比人埋身 打狗救人，組隊自衛，落街做文宣，fc先上Twitter。 我要真雙普選#:-[#mf\n</code>"},{"pid":"051e7064b870b7b7930ce15aa47642f85ea580e3","tid":1578330,"uid":15314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5ce5270a151b53866a9e5c276aea635e7384f1a8","tid":1578330,"uid":311275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:56:28.000Z","msg":"撕一貼十<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:00:06.000Z","msg":"認同呀！！！<br />\n但貼都要揀岩時候<br />\n由得班傻西921幫我地清舊文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">呢幾日整定啲新文宣到時慢慢貼</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60f431ef0526962bcf91ab0e1d76968e0a8860f8","tid":1578330,"uid":15314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:09:11.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"4f607ca375b7cb4dc75305b4152fb73eb145a713","tid":1578330,"uid":89011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:10:16.000Z","msg":"唔好晒時間搞藍絲<br />\n做返自己野<br />\n出去保護自己就得"},{"pid":"bf36953841acf0fee31f7c272643a64f60d89811","tid":1578330,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:10:53.000Z","msg":"好！"},{"pid":"b1fd7d06c41cbd461c4e9507ffd778ab28a8119f","tid":1578330,"uid":258784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:11:20.000Z","msg":"要黏多十倍"},{"pid":"ac21d3d18f42d623be50512a4ae5827df60bc2e4","tid":1578330,"uid":15314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4