爭資訊帶入社區<br />\n對方想摧毀佢<br />\n而我地又吹大雞去對陣既話<br />\n1. 對面傷幾多都好 我地傷一個都嫌多<br />\n2. POPO可以一舉大拘捕 介入呢啲打鬥亦可以挽回些少面子<br />\n3. 對家摧毀連儂牆只係一時 第二日咪貼返晒出黎<br />\n<br />\n無謂同對家短兵相接<br />\n根本對自己冇好處<br />\n我地唔係黑社會<br />\n唔係要霸地盤<br />\n佢地要撕就由佢撕<br />\n除非佢地郁我地手足<br />\n咁一定要自衛還拖"},{"pid":"917bd6e37447252a7ea71cb6da3e07e593747f54","tid":1578330,"uid":42740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T11:36:07.000Z","msg":"永遠唔好正面打<br />\n佢地有狗護送 <br />\n但落單又無狗既就<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59ce2f17d203daecc3070ac08befd2267cd47d7","tid":1578330,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong> <br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">如果機場係春袋 商場就係紅血球<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1573192\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1573192</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">和理塞 商場篇 <br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563867\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563867</a><br />\n</span>全<span style=\"color: violet;\">力攪商場攬炒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1569519\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1569519</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\">清算黨鐵商場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1571276\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1571276</a><br />\n</span><br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"8c0d5a8ddaaf1b6ae09158cf95a54465009d411d","tid":1578330,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2dc656ceba435f1d32d7f1a4070e5ec31975905","tid":1578330,"uid":2607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T12:49:09.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"f624441a8bf912687b765405472737b54302cec4","tid":1578330,"uid":291309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"repl